import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  
export const hello = 5;

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"hello-world"}}>{`Hello World`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
